s<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2010-12-24</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Israeli+says+UN+fans+the+flames+of+Middle+East+conflict&amp;rft.pub=New+York+Times&amp;rft.date=1983-10&amp;rft.au=Richard+Bernstein&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1983%2F10%2F04%2Fworld%2Fisraeli-says-un-fans-the-flames-of-middle-east-conflict.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AYehuda+Zvi+Blum\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> \"For decades now, Arab leaders have obstinately maintained that the whole region from the <a href=\"/wiki/Atlantic_Ocean\" title=\"Atlantic Ocean\">Atlantic Ocean</a> to the <a href=\"/wiki/Persian_Gulf\" title=\"Persian Gulf\">Persian Gulf</a> must be exclusively Arab, he said.\"</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-NYT-students-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-NYT-students_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/1983/05/10/world/israeli-envoy-at-un-scolds-133-us-jewish-law-students.html\">\"Israeli envoy at UN Scolds 133 Jewish Law Students\"</a>. New York Times. May 1983<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2010-12-24</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Israeli+envoy+at+UN+Scolds+133+Jewish+Law+Students&amp;rft.pub=New+York+Times&amp;rft.date=1983-05&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1983%2F05%2F10%2Fworld%2Fisraeli-envoy-at-un-scolds-133-us-jewish-law-students.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AYehuda+Zvi+Blum\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" ar